163
00:15:37,519 --> 00:15:40,063
Right, well, using layman's terms,

164
00:15:40,564 --> 00:15:42,774
we use a rotating magnetic field

165
00:15:42,858 --> 00:15:47,111
to focus a narrow beam of gravitons.
These in turn fold space-time,

166
00:15:47,196 --> 00:15:49,280
consistent with Weyl tensor dynamics,

167
00:15:49,365 --> 00:15:52,116
until the space-time curvature
becomes infinitely large

168
00:15:52,201 --> 00:15:54,702
and you produce a singularity.
Now, the singularity...

169
00:15:54,787 --> 00:15:56,537
Layman's terms.

170
00:15:56,622 --> 00:15:59,582
Fuck layman's terms.
