176
00:16:19,436 --> 00:16:22,522
Now, what's the shortest distance
between two points?

177
00:16:22,606 --> 00:16:24,065
A straight line.

178
00:16:24,817 --> 00:16:25,900
Wrong.

179
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:28,945
The shortest distance
between two points is zero.

180
00:16:29,071 --> 00:16:31,155
And that's what the gateway does.

181
00:16:31,407 --> 00:16:34,659
It folds space.

182
00:16:34,743 --> 00:16:39,497
So that point "A" and point "B" co-exist
in the same space and time.

183
00:16:40,457 --> 00:16:44,544
